        'Atome Malaysia explains its offering around 3 interest-free payments',
        'For some transactions, longer-tenure options may also be available with fees shown clearly in the app',
        'The first payment is made at the point of purchase, and the remaining payments are scheduled in the app',
        'For merchants, this adds another payment option at checkout',
      ],
      linkLabel: 'Refer to the official Atome Malaysia website',
