    },
    faq: {
      title: 'FAQ',
      mainItems: [
        {
          question: 'Is Novalink part of Atome?',
          answer:
            'No. Novalink supports merchant enquiry coordination and onboarding guidance. Novalink is not part of Atome’s internal team.',
        },
        {
          question: 'Is every business eligible?',
          answer: 'Not necessarily. Suitability depends on review and relevant requirements.',
        },
        {
          question: 'Does this enquiry guarantee approval?',
          answer: 'No. An initial enquiry does not guarantee approval. Eligibility and approval remain subject to review.',
        },
        {
          question: 'What information is needed to get started?',
          answer:
            'Usually basic information such as your business name, business type, location, and business channels.',
        },
        {
          question: 'Is there any fee to make an enquiry?',
          answer: 'There is no fee for an initial enquiry.',
        },
        {
          question: 'Do I need special hardware or integration?',
          answer:
            'Not necessarily. For physical stores, Atome uses a QR-based payment flow. For online stores, integration depends on your platform and sales channels.',
        },
        {
          question: 'Can my business appear in the Atome app?',
          answer:
            'Yes. Atome has the ability to feature merchants in the app, subject to their process and requirements.',
        },
        {
          question: 'Will every customer have the same spending limit?',
          answer:
            'No. Customer eligibility and spending limits can vary depending on the user profile, payment type, and Atome’s assessment.',
        },
        {
          question: 'How is merchant pricing determined?',
          answer:
            'There is no setup fee. Merchant pricing is based on MDR per transaction, and the commercial terms will be clarified during onboarding.',
        },
      ],
      supportLine:
        'Need help with fees, onboarding, business suitability, or online store requirements? WhatsApp us for an initial check.',
      moreTitle: 'More merchant questions',
      moreGroups: [
        {
          title: 'Fees & commercial terms',
          items: [
            {
              question: 'What makes Atome different from other pay-later options?',
              answer:
                'Atome is not just another checkout payment option. Merchants may also gain visibility inside the Atome app, benefit from selected campaigns or vouchers, and be more accessible to debit-card users who may not use credit cards.',
