              question: 'How many people use Atome?',
              answer:
                'Atome has a large user base in Malaysia and across the region. Beyond checkout, merchants may also gain visibility inside the Atome app.',
            },
            {
              question: 'What is the Atome fee?',
              answer:
                'For the merchants we typically handle, the fee structure we usually explain is 6% + RM1 per transaction. There is no setup fee and no monthly fee. Final confirmation remains subject to onboarding terms.',
            },
            {
              question: 'Can merchants get a lower rate than 6%?',
              answer:
                'Yes, in some cases. Merchants with high GMV, multiple branches, or strong brand profile may be able to negotiate a better rate with Atome.',
            },
            {
              question: 'Will every customer have the same credit limit?',
              answer:
                'No. Customer limits vary depending on the user profile, payment type, and repayment activity. Do not state fixed amounts on this page.',
            },
