            },
            {
              question: 'Can I apply if my business is outside Malaysia?',
              answer: 'No. Atome Malaysia only accepts businesses registered in Malaysia.',
            },
            {
              question: 'What if I run an online shop?',
              answer:
                'You may still apply, but your site should have a proper checkout page. In some cases, Atome may request screenshots or a live demo during assessment.',
            },
            {
              question: 'Will Atome ask for my product list?',
              answer:
                'Sometimes, especially during assessment. Merchants should be ready to provide SKU or product lists if requested.',
            },
            {
              question: 'What if my business is in a higher-risk category?',
              answer:
                'This may require a more thorough review. Atome may request additional documents or approvals depending on the business category.',
            },
          ],
        },
